cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CR 

The paper deals with deep reinforcement learning (RL) and safety, which are both topics that fall under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of RL in robotics (cs.RO) and safety-critical systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper evaluates its methods on a specific environment called CoinRun, which falls under the category of computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CR).
